<section class="pt-32">
  <div class="max-w-[1172px] px-4 h-full mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl text-center font-title text-blue-600 mb-8">
      About Us
    </h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col flex-wrap justify-center">
      <div class="parallax_1 flex items-center lg:flex-row flex-col py-6">
        <div
          class="overflow-hidden relative flex-1 lg:h-[400px] max-h-[400px] w-full rounded-2xl"
        >
          <img
            src="images/about1.jpg"
            alt="about image 1"
            class="img relative lg:absolute top-0 left-0 h-[800px] w-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <p
          class="about_text about_text_trigger_1 flex-1 font-body leading-6 font-medium text-gray-500 mx-4 my-6 text-xl text-justify uppercase"
        >
          Aravan Cargo Inc., established in 2016 in Joliet, Illinois, is your
          trusted partner on the journey to vehicle ownership. We have evolved
          into a premier full-service logistics company, servicing all 48
          continental states. Dedicated to delivering dependable service and
          ensuring customer satisfaction, we have assisted numerous drivers in
          transitioning from company drivers to successful fleet
          owner-operators. In fact, a dozen drivers have successfully launched
          their own trucking businesses with our support.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="parallax_2 flex items-center lg:flex-row-reverse flex-col py-6"
      >
        <div
          class="overflow-hidden relative flex-1 lg:h-[400px] max-h-[400px] w-full rounded-2xl"
        >
          <img
            src="images/about2.jpg"
            alt="about image 1"
            class="img relative lg:absolute top-0 left-0 h-[800px] w-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <p
          class="about_text about_text_trigger_2 flex-1 font-body leading-6 font-medium text-gray-500 mx-4 my-6 text-xl text-justify uppercase"
        >
          For aspiring truck drivers seeking self-employment, Aravan Cargo Inc.
          is a trusted ally, helping individuals achieve their entrepreneurial
          goals. With our proven expertise, thorough support, and professional
          guidance, we enable trucking professionals to attain financial
          independence in the dynamic transportation industry.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

